1. Project ka Goal
Ye ek chhota sa management software hoga jisme tum students ke records manage kar sakte ho (jaise ek chhoti database).
Matlab:

Student ka naam, roll number, age, marks save karna

Unko screen pe dikhana

Search karna

Update karna

Delete karna

Aur ye sab file mein bhi save rahe, taki program band karke dubara chalane par data wapas mil jaye.

2. Main Menu (Program ka control center)
Jab user program run karega, usse options milenge:

Add Student

Display All Students

Search Student

Update Student

Delete Student

Exit

Ye menu bar-bar loop mein chalega jab tak user Exit nahi choose karta.

3. Features ek ek karke
(a) Add Student
User se details mangni hain (Name, Roll No, Age, Marks).

Inko ek structure (struct) ke andar store karna hai.

Phir is record ko list ya file mein save karna hai.

(b) Display All
Saare students ke records ek sath screen par print karna.

Agar file handling use kar rahe ho to file se read karke dikhana.

(c) Search Student
User roll number ya naam enter karega.

Tumhe data mein us record ko dhundna hoga.

Agar mila to details show kar do, warna â€œNot Foundâ€ likho.

(d) Update Student
Pehle search karna hai record.

Agar record mil jaye to user se new details lo (jaise marks change karne hain ya age update karni hai).

Fir updated data save kar do.

(e) Delete Student
Pehle record search karna hai.

Agar mila to us record ko hata do (file/array se).

Agar array use ho raha hai to baaki records shift karne padenge.

(f) Exit
Program close karna.

File use ho rahi hai to ensure karna ke saara data properly save ho gaya.

4. Concepts Jo Tum Practice Karoge
Structures (struct) â†’ ek student ke record ko group karne ke liye.

Arrays / Linked List â†’ ek se zyada students ko memory mein store karne ke liye.

File Handling â†’ data ko permanent save karne ke liye (fopen, fread, fwrite).

Functions â†’ har kaam ke liye alag function (add, display, searchâ€¦).

Loops & Conditions â†’ menu repeat karna aur choices check karna.

5. Optional Add-ons (Extra Features)
Students ko marks ya name ke hisaab se sort karna.

Class average marks calculate karna.

Admin ke liye password protection lagana.

