ğŸ”¹ 1. Student ka naam, roll number, age, marks save karna
Ye data user se input lena hai (scanf se).

Fir usko ek structure ke andar store karna hai.

Us record ko file ke andar save karna hai.

Kitne students? â†’ Jitne user chahe. Har baar jab user "Add Student" select karega, ek naya record file ke end mein append ho jayega.

ğŸ‘‰ Matlab limit fix nahi hai. Tum jitne chahe students add kar sakte ho.

ğŸ”¹ 2. Unko screen pe dikhana (Display All Students)
Jab user "Display All" choose karega:

File ko read mode (r) mein open karo.

File ke andar jitne records hain, unhe ek ek karke read karo.

Har record ko printf ke zariye screen par show kar do.

ğŸ‘‰ Tum poore students ek sath dekh loge.
Isliye chahe tum ek student add karo ya 50, sab file mein store rahenge aur display option pe sab print ho jayenge.

ğŸ”¹ 3. Search karna
User input dega (Roll Number ya Name).

File ko read mode mein open karo.

Har record ko ek ek read karo aur compare karo:

Agar match mil gaya to details screen pe print kar do.

Agar file ke end tak nahi mila to "Not Found" print kar do.

ğŸ‘‰ Ye search hamesha file ke andar hi hoti hai.

ğŸ”¹ 4. Update karna
Pehle search karna hoga (Roll ya Name se).

Agar record mil gaya:

User se naya data input lo (jaise new marks, age).

Ek temporary file banao.

Purani file ko read karo:

Jo record match nahi karta, usko as it is copy karo.

Jo record match karta, usko updated details ke sath save karo.

End mein purani file delete karo aur temporary file ko original file ka naam de do.

ğŸ‘‰ Is tarah update ho jata hai.

ğŸ”¹ 5. Delete karna
Delete bhi update ki tarah hota hai.

Pehle search karo (Roll/Name).

Ek temporary file banao.

Purani file ke saare records ek ek read karo:

Agar record delete karna hai â†’ usko skip kar do.

Baaki sab records temporary file mein copy kar do.

End mein purani file delete kar do aur temporary file ko uska naam de do.

 6 for exit